caption:
Let’s have a BBQ 🍔🌭
-
Saturday, July 15th, we eat! 🙌🏼
-
This time instead of a photo walk we’d like to get everyone together for a few hours of photography, food & fun under the sun. We did a BBQ about 3 years ago & it was a great time so we’d like to do this before our next walk.
-
We will be selling tickets for $5 just to cover the cost of food. There are only 40 spots available. Tickets go on sale today at 3:00pm, link in bio.
-
We look forward to seeing you again soon! 🫶🏼🔌

Thank you to everyone that attended TPP Stamford! 📷⛪️
Haven’t had a chance to sit & edit but better late than never!
-
Our first meet in 2 years & it rained BUT that didn’t stop a bunch of creatives from pullin up! Thank you all for the incredible support.
-
Please use #ThePhotoPlug & tag us in your posts so we can see your work! Selecting a winner for the $25 @milfordphoto giftcard this Saturday! Much love everyone ❤️ 
-
See you soon! Stay plugged in 🔌

The time for a Photo Plug walk has come once again📸🔌
-
It’s been 2 long years since we have had a meet up. Saturday, May 20th, we return 🙏🏻

📍 MEETUP LOCATION: First Presbyterian Church 
🕰️ TIME: 10:00am - 1:30pm
💰 COST: Free free free 
-
As usual this event is 100% free & open to photographers, models & creatives of all skill levels. This is a networking event for you to meet people that share the same passions as you. As always we’ll have a route to do a short photo walk. We will be at the church for about an hour & a half then we start walking towards downtown Stamford & as usual we’ll stop somewhere to get food afterwards 🍽️
POST THIS ON YOUR STORIES! The more you share, the bigger the turnout! Let’s comeback with a bang 🤝🏼
-
Check our highlights to see what we’ve done in the past. We’d love to add new people to our big family ❤️

Yall never let us down 💪🏼🔌
-
Huge thank you to all the creatives that attended The Photo Plug: Hartford this weekend! On 3 days notice you pulled up with the same incredible energy as always. We love and appreciate you all ❤️ 
-
Please tag us and use the hashtag #TPPHartford so we can see your work and select winners for the @allazoclothing , @bodeusa , @milfordphoto , & @mobymav giveaways! 🎁 
-
We will be selecting our top photos on 12/1 and put them on our story for you all to vote and select winners fairly.
-
Thank you again and remember, you are the plug 🔌
#TPPHartford

Ladies and gentlemen, this Saturday, The Photo Plug is back 📸🔌
-
It’s been 2 years since we all got to come together so let’s make it happen. This Saturday from 12:00PM - 5:00PM The Photo Plug will be in Downtown Hartford, CT. 📍
-
Our sponsors @milfordphoto , @bodeusa , @allazoclothing , and @mobymav will be giving away prizes to the top selected photos from the meet. 🎁 
-
This networking event is free and open to photographers and models of all skill levels. If you haven’t been to a Photo Plug event then go check our highlights and feed to see just how great they are. SHARE THIS POST to stories and let’s show everyone that we outside! 🙏🏻
-
See you all Saturday 🔌

Thank you to everyone that pulled up yesterday! We hope you had a good time and safe travels. See you again soon fam! 🙏🏻🔌❤️
-
Comment where you want us to go next!

Boston, we’re back 🔌
-
October 26th we’ll be meeting up once again for a photo walk at the Reflection Pool in Boston, MA. As usual we’ll wait 1 hour (until 3PM) for everyone to arrive and then we’re going on a 30 minute walk to Acorn st, passing other sites along the way, and then back. 🚶🏻‍♂️🚶🏽‍♀️🤳
-
Make sure you RSVP (link in bio)
We hope to see familiar faces and lots of new ones! See you soon, Boston 🙏🏻

Comment YEEERRRRRRR!
Thank yall for poppin out once again! Always a fun time full of laughs when we link up. Can’t wait for the next one. Much love family! PLUG LIFE 🙏🏻❤️🔌
Big thanks to those that came out to model for the day and HUGE thank you to @thegreenlightpodcast @createthemood & @milfordphoto for sponsoring once again! 👏🏼
& big shout out to @_ralfy for working the grill all day 💪🏼

Who will we see there?? Comment below 👇🏼
-
Let’s have a great day to end the summer. Come out and relax or adventure around the park and shoot 📷
-
This event is sponsored by @milfordphoto which will be giving away a $25 giftcard, @thegreenlightpodcast team will be there doing a podcast and @createthemood will document the day 🔌
-
This event is RSVP only. RSVP is required which will be $5 through the link in our bio. This fee is to help pay for food and the picnic shelter we rented out for the day.
-
We look forward to seeing you soon 🙏🏻🏖

Congratulations @stevewalterphoto ! 👏🏼🎊
After careful consideration and searching through all the amazing photos from the New Haven meet, we have decided to select @stevewalterphoto ‘s set of @hperuccio to be the winner of the @milfordphoto giftcard! Beautiful lighting, natural poses and real emotion. We love it! Great job Steve and Haili! 📷🔌
-
See you guys next month 🙏🏻
You guys are the best!!! We’ll have next month’s meet announced soon. Thank you for the support and plugging in with us every month 🙏🏻🔌

Thank you to everyone that came out to New Haven yesterday! 🙏🏻
As always it was an amazing time. Thank you to every talented photographer and every beautiful model that came out to make some magic!! We ❤️ you all 🔌.
HUGE thanks to @thegreenlightpodcast & @milfordphoto for sponsoring! Be sure to hashtag #ThePhotoPlug and tag us so we can see your work! We will select a winner for the $25 @milfordphoto giftcard on Friday May 31st.
Once again we apologize for the inconvenience at Lighthouse Point Park, it was unexpected and out of our control.
Video by the amazing @createthemood ! 🎥
